OL,4,G0340FDrop The Dead Donkey
OL,5,     GIt's party time for GlobeLink:
OL,6,     Gthe razz at the British News
OL,7,     GAwards ceremony begins. Damian
OL,8,     Gdreams of victory, Dave dreams of
OL,9,     GHelen, and for once Henry is less
OL,10,     Gthan happy to be centre-stage.
OL,11,G0405FDrop The Dead Donkey
OL,12,     GAfter a sudden death at
OL,13,     GGlobeLink, Gus goes into exercise
OL,14,     Goverdrive to try to defer his own
OL,15,     Gdemise. Meanwhile, George tries
OL,16,     Ghis hand at acting; and Damien
OL,17,     Ghas trouble with his Porsche.
OL,18,G0430FStereo Underground
OL,19,     GRichard Latto presents
OL,20,     Galternative anthems from a music
OL,21,     Gcommunity with attitude.
